      <title>萨姆·奥特曼加入新旧金山市长过渡团队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/sam-altman-joins-transition-team-for-new-san-francisco-mayor-daniel-lurie</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山市长候任者丹尼尔·鲁里（Daniel Lurie）组建了一个过渡团队，其中包括 OpenAI 联合创始人萨姆·奥特曼（Sam Altman），利用有影响力的当地领导人，让这位政治新人掌控该市的官僚机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/sam-altman-joins-transition-team-for-new-san-francisco-mayor-daniel-lurie</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:26:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约交通局批准征收 9 美元拥堵费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/new-york-s-transit-agency-approves-9-congestion-pricing-toll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大都会运输署批准了曼哈顿的交通拥堵收费修改计划，但当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁称，一旦上任，他将终止该计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/new-york-s-transit-agency-approves-9-congestion-pricing-toll</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:17:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即使美国采取行动，德国也不会向乌克兰提供远程导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/germany-won-t-give-ukraine-long-range-missile-even-after-us-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国已决定授权基辅使用其武器袭击俄罗斯境内，但德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨仍为其不向乌克兰提供金牛座远程导弹的决定进行辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/germany-won-t-give-ukraine-long-range-missile-even-after-us-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:16:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦在欧盟公投后改组政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/moldova-reshuffles-government-after-tight-eu-referendum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦亲西方总统承诺在欧盟成员国资格公投后进行内阁改组，随后该国总理宣布内阁阵容发生变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/moldova-reshuffles-government-after-tight-eu-referendum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普就任前美国将对更多以色列强硬派定居者实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/us-sanctions-more-hardline-israeli-settlers-before-trump-s-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将离任的拜登-哈里斯政府对占领区约旦河西岸的以色列极端定居者实施了更多制裁，而当选总统唐纳德·特朗普及其提名人可能会撤销这些制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/us-sanctions-more-hardline-israeli-settlers-before-trump-s-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 17:36:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰领导人称肖尔茨正在破坏特朗普结束战争的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/poland-s-leader-says-scholz-is-undermining-trump-push-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰国家元首表示，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨正试图将唐纳德·特朗普排除在乌克兰未来谈判之外，以恢复德国与克里姆林宫的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/poland-s-leader-says-scholz-is-undermining-trump-push-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 17:32:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刺激措施和特朗普关税导致交易员逃离中国 ETF，导致资金大量流失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/china-etfs-bleed-cash-as-traders-flee-on-stimulus-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着人们对中国经济增长前景以及唐纳德·特朗普政府实施新关税的风险的担忧日益加剧，购买中国股票的交易所交易基金 (ETF) 持续出现资金外流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/china-etfs-bleed-cash-as-traders-flee-on-stimulus-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 17:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队支持沃什，尽管财政部之争持续存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/trump-team-shows-support-for-warsh-as-treasury-feuding-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的一些主要顾问表示支持前美联储理事凯文·沃什担任下一任财政部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/trump-team-shows-support-for-warsh-as-treasury-feuding-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 15:45:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将请求超过 980 亿美元的紧急救灾资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/biden-budget-chief-urges-congress-to-pass-disaster-relief-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的政府正在向国会寻求超过 980 亿美元的紧急救灾资金，以应对最近接连袭击美国东南部并造成数十亿美元损失的飓风造成的破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/biden-budget-chief-urges-congress-to-pass-disaster-relief-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默在 G20 峰会上就人权问题与习近平对峙。结果并不顺利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/starmer-to-meet-xi-using-growth-push-to-justify-uk-china-thaw</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 刚刚向中国国家主席习近平表达了英国对香港一名报纸出版商入狱的困境的担忧，英国媒体就被突然赶出了房间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/starmer-to-meet-xi-using-growth-push-to-justify-uk-china-thaw</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
